				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Astarion bit Gale in gameplay. Astarion got poisoned, a short dialog between Gale and Astarion. Several possible lines:\r\n1. Party doesn't know that Astarion is a vampire. Astarion shocked Gale's blood is like bile, Gale shocked Astarion is a vampire.\r\n2. Party knows Astarion is a vampire and he tried to bite Gale during a camp night. Gale mocks him a bit - \"you don't learn, do you?\"\r\n3. Party knows Astarion is a vampire, but he hasn't bitten Gale yet. Astarion is surprised by Gale's blood, Gale tells him think before biting other people."
				}
